{"tid":1458432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致曱甴們","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:13:59.000Z","uid":110665,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eafac649d621b4ecc801cb8dbc0ccdd0e757b7b4","tid":1458432,"uid":110665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對唔住 話你哋係曱甴 你哋喺我最敬愛嘅兄弟姊妹</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我想你哋認真睇一睇</span> <br />\n經過811 我想你哋了解一下 黑警已經殺紅了眼 我哋要諗嘅係究竟點行落去 <span style=\"color: red;\">升級？</span> 暫時我睇唔到大家有勇氣去升級 睇落去就會明<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">留喺原地？</span>咁我哋應該要有陣法 <span style=\"color: red;\">人</span>我哋係好多 但前線我哋真係無啦 <br />\n811尖沙咀 深水埗 有好多前線犧牲<br />\n人逼人 無空位俾前線走 我覺得要留位比前排走 <br />\n因為個個口講都係話自己用前途將來嚟博 的確係 但抱住僥倖嘅態度 捉唔到你就無事 反而有必死之心嘅都比你哋頂死哂 因為一轉身全部人喺度走緊 但又唔係走得快 仲嗌乜撚嘢12 12踏步走 速龍距離我5個身位 仲要前面12 12 我真係寧願幾個街口後面先有人 <br />\n一係就唔好淆底 永遠佢出速龍 我哋不退反攻 但機會不大</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家幫我推上去</span>"},{"pid":"a1e9e901e4ccacde4cca409bb0914a5aae1b7e9b","tid":1458432,"uid":110665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"2b54ad0b9275e6a2befc6a8b070eb2a27cb0ae67","tid":1458432,"uid":110665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"a6bb1b27ab3d8e785e1f85759666bf9ac00c4e2a","tid":1458432,"uid":110665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"e0182f63cd0af2517e3c25d7edad9c99c6490f1d","tid":1458432,"uid":110665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:04:17.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"13813bd5ac24eb2d9506ad9f66b98b18c3ed1f02","tid":1458432,"uid":110665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"ae43dc18046328c975b5abd006fbb9c3903a6073","tid":1458432,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,